{"tid":594340,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"星座真係一樣好濕鳩嘅野","createTime":"2018-03-15T18:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T14:31:30.000Z","uid":174603,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b25fb52da16067dc48494700a52602e51598377","tid":594340,"uid":174603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T18:04:43.000Z","msg":"一個人嘅性格同運氣會由佢幾月出生決定？<br />\n<br />\n對唔同星座嘅人嘅描述其實放係唔同人身上 佢地都9成都覺得中，個啲咩「缺乏安全感」、「外表堅強但都有軟弱時候」，係我眼中同「水瓶座嘅人阿媽係女人」無分別。<br />\n<br />\n有人會話其實某程度上算係一種統計學，都算科學。ok，咁就講科學。咁我就想問sample嚟自邊到？咩國家或者地區嘅人？佢地嘅文化又有可能會影響性格/價值觀㗎喎。仲有，拎咗幾多人做sample？係幾多年前嘅事？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星座<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8e1da1dc53dd3181c7556c1eec7f960eb776f7","tid":594340,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T18:07:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d29a8493421cac38d9b8fa3865cd12e74b31745","tid":594340,"uid":174603,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T18:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/16/020801_57022a38b989f935fc77cfd8d3480752.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F020801_57022a38b989f935fc77cfd8d3480752.png&h=50f9ab7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399273471f0e5aade465bc7d95196d3804957696","tid":594340,"uid":174603,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e8e1da1dc53dd3181c7556c1eec7f960eb776f7","tid":594340,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T18:07:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T18:08:48.000Z","msg":"信嘅人多的是"},{"pid":"ba616bba80ee39431e0a31c8df5a76ef230541dd","tid":594340,"uid":14073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":